<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.5">
<l>tūmpuṭait tiṇkaivaṉ tāḷkaḷiṟ ṟiṉtuyar tīrttara vamveru vamuṉanāḷ</l>
<l>pūmpuṉal poykaipuk kāṉava ṉukkiṭan tāṉtaṭañ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>tēmpoḻil kuṉṟeyil teṉṉava ṉaitticaip pacceru mēlviyan taṉṟuceṉṟa</l>
<l>pāmpuṭaip pallavar kōṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by ponds, the very place of him who once</l>
<l rend="indent">plunged into a pool of fresh water so that the serpent feared [him],</l>
<l>Having allayed the misery of the elephant with powerful legs</l>
<l rend="indent">and a strong, hollow trunk,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the king of the Pallavas</l>
<l rend="indent">with a serpent [banner],</l>
<l>Who proudly went that day onto the battlefield to beset the southerner,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose hill fort has honeyed gardens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
